One person was killed while 11 others sustained various degrees of injuries in an accident that occurred on Saturday along the Awka-Onitsha expressway by Enugwu Agidi junction of Anambra State. The accident involved a commercial bus with Reg.No:463 XB and Mitsubishi L 300 bus with Reg.No:XC 418 JJT . Anambra State Police Public Relations Officer, SP Haruna Mohammed, who confirmed the incident in a press release issued to journalists in Awka, on Sunday,Â  said the police patrol team attached to Abagana Division had visited the scene and rushed casualties to an Orthopaedic hospital at Ngozika Estate and the Odumegwu Ojukwu Teaching Hospital, Awka, for treatment.